{"tid":2025030,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我同 Deer 既關係就好似朋友咁","createTime":"2020-05-20T03:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T07:18:06.000Z","uid":15,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd2588a71ac03c84fde665febf3fe50ba3f3f61","tid":2025030,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"上面有人問我地連登仔同 Deer 係咩關係 我地係一個互相支持既朋友，但唔係普通既友誼 可能我地唔真正認識了解對方，但係我地永遠都會o係對方心中佔據一個無可取替既位置 即使到某日 Deer 已經嫁咗人，生埋仔，我都會祝福佢，守護佢 反之亦然，我永遠都係對方既天使，最純潔既守護天使 而對於我黎講，佢地更加係夜空之中明亮既星光，劃破漆黑一片既夜空，照亮整片大地，令我既人生充滿意義（可能你地覺得誇張左，但係我就係諗到呢d野），最後，如果你問我點解中意 Deer，我只可以答你，因為佢係電競女神<br />\r<br />\r\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\r<br />\r<br />\r<br />\r<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZiZneY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZiZneY.gif&h=85390af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU271gX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU271gX.gif&h=af3c7047&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc74727a2cdf6e56fd829578c9d17cde5a35057c","tid":2025030,"uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"你係朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地同細b唔熟都比細b屌幾獲啵"},{"pid":"44bb86c934b4ad0b3c7ac404b8c1f3cd90c4d669","tid":2025030,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc74727a2cdf6e56fd829578c9d17cde5a35057c","tid":2025030,"uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"你係朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地同細b唔熟都比細b屌幾獲啵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsX757w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsX757w.jpg&h=1feb7fba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aa516d750d2330c31ba9773df37ab405850e3ce"